headline: Aon Launches Aon Broker Copilot to Modernize Insurance Placement with AI and Data at Scale
summary: Aon plc (NYSE: AON), a leading global professional services firm, today announced the launch of Aon Broker Copilot, a proprietary, patent-pending platform that uses artificial intelligence, large-language models and predictive analytics to transform the commercial insurance placement process.
